title: BRIEF-Woodford Investment Says Will Be Working With Prothena Corp On Its Strategy Beyond Its Pronto Trial Investigating NEOd001 In Al Amyloidosis
text:
Market News April 23, 2018 / 1:40 PM / Updated 30 minutes ago BRIEF-Woodford Investment Says Will Be Working With Prothena Corp On Its Strategy Beyond Its Pronto Trial Investigating NEOd001 In Al Amyloidosis Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 23 (Reuters) - Prothena Corporation PLC: 
* WOODFORD INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT SAYS WILL BE WORKING WITH PROTHENA CORP ON ITS STRATEGY BEYOND ITS PRONTO TRIAL INVESTIGATING NEOD001 IN AL AMYLOIDOSIS Source text: ( bit.ly/2HRH9mk ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
